     <div type="poem">
   <head>At {y}r h{y}gar Dharlhennydh.</head>
   <l>LH{y}ma g{y}{w}irgarn lhom-iaith!</l>
   <l>Lh{y}ma‘r g{w}ir nid lh{w}m y{w}‘r g{w}aith;</l>
   <l>Budhiol i ba{w}b ond b{y}dhar,</l>
   <l>Iaith g{y}{w}ir gu a‘th g{w}ir gar.</l>
   <l>Rheidiol i bob dyn rhodiad</l>
   <l>G{w}ann a gle{w} {y}nn g{w}eini‘n g{w}lad.</l>
   <l>Rheidiol i dhalht {y}r hudau</l>
   <l>Ar araith goeth, g{y}nlhaith, gau;</l>
   <l>Bid gair Du{w}; bid o g{w}r doeth;</l>
   <l>Bid o {y}nni bod anoeth.</l>
   <l>Cann h{y}nny, can{w}n {y}na</l>
   <l>Bha{w}l i Dhu{w}, o ‘orbholedh dha.</l>
   <l>Ar ber{w}a{w}d moler Perri</l>
   <l>{W}raidh na{w}s, a‘neurodh Ni,</l>
   <l>O dr{w}ssio ‘r iaith, a dreisied;</l>
   <l>O‘r le{w}ch a‘i th{y}nny ar lhed,</l>
   <l>{Y}n g{w}yraidh ag {y}n g{y}rrith,</l>
   <l>{Y}n bhy{w} {y}nn ei rby{w} a‘i rhith.</l>
   <p>H. Sal.</p>
</div>
